You can&#39;t put li tags inside a select tag. 
In the select tag, you can only put option tags.
consider this: 
    
    &lt;select&gt;
        &lt;option&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#tab01&quot;&gt;Billing Details&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/option&gt;
